10 Membership of the Homeland Security Advisory Council”
11 Amend the bill by striking out everything after the enacting clause and inserting the
12 following:
13 'Sec. 1. 37-B MRSA §708, sub-§1, as amended by PL 2011, c. 529, §1 and
14 amended by c. 657, Pt. W, §6, is further amended to read:
15 1. Membership. The council is composed of the following 9 11 members:
16 A. The director or the director's designee;
17 B. The Commissioner of Defense, Veterans and Emergency Management or the
18 commissioner's designee;
19 C. The Commissioner of Public Safety or the commissioner's designee;
20 D. The Director of the Maine Center for Disease Control and Prevention within the
21 Department of Health and Human Services or the director's designee;
22 E. The Chief of the State Police within the Department of Public Safety or the chief's
23 designee;
24 F. A representative of the Governor;
25 G. The Commissioner of Inland Fisheries and Wildlife or the commissioner's designee;
